    "body": "It would be great if Electron could create shortcuts on Windows.\n\nAt present I am using a few `.vbs` shell scripts if that helps anyone:\n\n### resolve-special-folder.vbs\n\nResolve the location of a special system folder which is dependent on user language (accepts 1 argument: name of special folder - see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special_folder - and writes resolved path to stdout):\n\n```\nWScript.Echo WScript.CreateObject(\"Wscript.Shell\").SpecialFolders(WScript.Arguments.Item(0))\n```\n\n### create-shortcut.vbs\n\nCreate a shortcut (accepts 4 arguments: shortcut path, target path, icon location, working directory):\n\n```\nset WshShell = WScript.CreateObject(\"WScript.Shell\")\nset oShellLink = WshShell.CreateShortcut(WScript.Arguments.Item(0))\noShellLink.TargetPath = WScript.Arguments.Item(1)\noShellLink.IconLocation = WScript.Arguments.Item(2)\noShellLink.WorkingDirectory = WScript.Arguments.Item(3)\noShellLink.Save\n```\n"
  },
